<DIV style="position:absolute;top:257;left:90"><nobr><span class="ft16">About this manual</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:308;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">This manual is intended to cover the full range of requirements for<br>anyone wishing to install, use, or configure the Easysoft ODBC-<br>ODBC Bridge (OOB). Supplementary information is provided for<br>those wishing to build ODBC applications that link through a driver<br>manager, but please note that this manual is not an ODBC<br>programming manual.</span></nobr></DIV>
