<DIV style="position:absolute;top:233;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">Windows 95, 98, 2000, NT, XP, ME or 2003 Server, which are<br>trademarks of the Microsoft Corporation. The X Window system is<br>specifically excluded from this and is referred to as</span></nobr></DIV>
