<DIV style="position:absolute;top:386;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">for thread-safe versions).</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:529;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">Unix filenames may also be suffixed with</span></nobr></DIV>
