<DIV style="position:absolute;top:185;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft3">is running.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:221;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft3">b) a username and password to logon to the operating system on</span></nobr></DIV>
