<DIV style="position:absolute;top:347;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft22"><b>License to use</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:374;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">There are two license agreement files provided in the distribution;<br>one that applies if you are installing just the OOB Client, and another<br>that applies if you are installing the OOB Server or both the OOB<br>Client and Server. The license text can be found in the files</span></nobr></DIV>
