<DIV style="position:absolute;top:470;left:765"><nobr><span class="ft3">.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:494;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">Determine which applies to you and be sure to understand the terms<br>before continuing as you will be required to accept the license terms<br>at the start of the installation.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:584;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft22"><b>Answering questions during the installation</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:611;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">Throughout the installation, you will be asked to supply the answer<br>to some questions. In each case, the default will be displayed in<br>square brackets and you need only press</span></nobr></DIV>
