<DIV style="position:absolute;top:683;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft6">default. If there are alternative responses, these will be shown in<br>round brackets; to pick one of these type them and press</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:709;left:719"><nobr><span class="ft18">&lt;Enter&gt;</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:707;left:794"><nobr><span class="ft3">.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:740;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">For example:</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:775;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">Do you want to continue? (y/n) [n]:</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:806;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">The possible answers to this question are &quot;</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:808;left:603"><nobr><span class="ft18">y</span></nobr></DIV>
