<DIV style="position:absolute;top:158;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft22"><b>Running the installer</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:185;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">Before you run the installer, make sure you have read the</span></nobr></DIV>
