<DIV style="position:absolute;top:305;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">user. If you are concerned about the changes that will be made to<br>your system, see</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:329;left:402"><nobr><span class="ft4"><b>&quot;Changes made to your system&quot; on page 61</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:329;left:778"><nobr><span class="ft3">.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:362;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">To start the installation run:</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:397;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">./install</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:428;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">You will need to:</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:461;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">•</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:461;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft3">Confirm your acceptance of the license agreement with &quot;</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:463;left:738"><nobr><span class="ft18">yes</span></nobr></DIV>
