<DIV style="position:absolute;top:754;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft18">/usr/local/easysoft/oob/doc</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:785;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft3">The OOB manual (this manual) in PDF format.</span></nobr></DIV>
</DIV>
