<DIV style="position:absolute;top:190;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">xinetd</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:188;left:330"><nobr><span class="ft3">uses a configuration file of</span></nobr></DIV>
