<DIV style="position:absolute;top:470;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge service settings.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:503;left:222"><nobr><span class="ft3">12. There are therefore two ways to delete the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC</span></nobr></DIV>
