<DIV style="position:absolute;top:736;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">&lt;InstallDir&gt;/easysoft/lib</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:767;left:222"><nobr><span class="ft3">17. If you are no longer using unixODBC then you can also remove the</span></nobr></DIV>
