<DIV style="position:absolute;top:227;left:473"><nobr><span class="ft17"><b>SOURCE</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:257;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">Before setting up the OOB Client, the new data source and the OOB<br>Server setup should be verified with either an ODBC application<br>available on your Unix machine or the unixODBC</span></nobr></DIV>
