<DIV style="position:absolute;top:158;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft23"><b>Example 1: Check the OOB Server is running on the correct</b><br><b>machine and listening on the correct port</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:205;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">oobping</span></nobr></DIV>
