<DIV style="position:absolute;top:328;left:304"><nobr><span class="ft18">Host: myserver, Port: 8888</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:361;left:304"><nobr><span class="ft18">Attempting connection...OK</span></nobr></DIV>
