<DIV style="position:absolute;top:791;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">(size=256)</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:823;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">If there is nothing listening on the specified port then you will get a<br>connection refused error and you should check that the OOB Server<br>is running and is configured to use the specified port.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:500;left:279"><nobr><span class="ft11"><b>NB</b></span></nobr></DIV>
