<DIV style="position:absolute;top:158;left:494"><nobr><span class="ft3">and</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:160;left:528"><nobr><span class="ft18">-p</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:158;left:555"><nobr><span class="ft3">attributes you can work out the</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:182;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">extra time required to perform the operating system logon:</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:217;left:291"><nobr><span class="ft18">oobping -e -h myserver -u myosuser -p mypassword</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:250;left:304"><nobr><span class="ft18">Host: myserver, Port: 8888</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:283;left:304"><nobr><span class="ft18">Attempting connection...OK</span></nobr></DIV>
