<DIV style="position:absolute;top:314;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">To connect the OOB Client in Unix to a remote data source, you<br>need to define the data source on the remote machine by specifying<br>its attributes in a data source on the local (client) machine.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:395;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">You can create a data source for the OOB Client on the local Unix<br>machine either by:</span></nobr></DIV>
