<DIV style="position:absolute;top:536;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">The demonstration program is self-explanatory: select an option,<br>press</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:560;left:310"><nobr><span class="ft3">&lt;Enter&gt; and then follow the information displayed on screen.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:593;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">[1] displays the initial notice.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:626;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">[2] displays the requirements for the demo.</span></nobr></DIV>
