<DIV style="position:absolute;top:716;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">through the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:749;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">[5] retrieves a table from the database on</span></nobr></DIV>
