<DIV style="position:absolute;top:749;left:777"><nobr><span class="ft3">.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:827;left:280"><nobr><span class="ft11"><b>NB</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:782;left:343"><nobr><span class="ft6">Option 5 will only retrieve data when your demo data<br>source is configured to connect to the</span></nobr></DIV>
