<DIV style="position:absolute;top:397;left:648"><nobr><span class="ft3">). The connection</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:421;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">string is displayed in full before the demo program attempts to<br>connect using that connection string.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:478;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft6">[8] displays suggestions as to what may be the problem with your<br>connection.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:535;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">[9] exits from the demo program.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:260;left:280"><nobr><span class="ft11"><b>NB</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:239;left:343"><nobr><span class="ft5">If a data source points to a machine that cannot currently<br>be contacted, the connection attempt may take a couple<br>of minutes to time out.</span></nobr></DIV>
