<DIV style="position:absolute;top:692;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">When ON (set to 1 or checked), the</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:694;left:549"><nobr><span class="ft18">MetaDataBlockFetch</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:692;left:748"><nobr><span class="ft3">option</span></nobr></DIV>
