<DIV style="position:absolute;top:502;left:704"><nobr><span class="ft18">UID</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:500;left:741"><nobr><span class="ft3">and</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:526;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft18">PWD</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:524;left:298"><nobr><span class="ft3">values passed from the application in the connection string and</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:548;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">use the</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:550;left:325"><nobr><span class="ft18">TargetUser</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:548;left:438"><nobr><span class="ft3">and</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:550;left:473"><nobr><span class="ft18">TargetAuth</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:548;left:586"><nobr><span class="ft3">values for</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:550;left:669"><nobr><span class="ft18">UID</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:548;left:701"><nobr><span class="ft3">/</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:550;left:706"><nobr><span class="ft18">PWD</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:548;left:738"><nobr><span class="ft3">.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:581;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">This option may need to be selected for some software (e.g. Crystal<br>Info which passes an empty</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:607;left:484"><nobr><span class="ft18">PWD</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:605;left:521"><nobr><span class="ft3">field and expects the driver to issue</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:629;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft6">a prompt dialog box), but this is not always possible when the driver<br>is on a remote machine.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:686;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">The default for</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:688;left:382"><nobr><span class="ft18">Override UID/PWD</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:686;left:559"><nobr><span class="ft3">is off (0).</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:299;left:267"><nobr><span class="ft19"><b>Interface</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:299;left:451"><nobr><span class="ft19"><b>Value</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:329;left:267"><nobr><span class="ft3">DSN Dialogue Box</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:329;left:451"><nobr><span class="ft3">MetaDataBlockFetch</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:362;left:267"><nobr><span class="ft3">odbc.ini file (Unix)</span></nobr></DIV>
