<DIV style="position:absolute;top:191;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft5">To add another fallback OOB Server, click <b>Add</b>, then repeat<br>steps 6 and 7.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:248;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">•</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:248;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft6">If you’ve finished adding OOB Servers, click <b>Test </b>to test the<br>connection process for each server in the list.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:305;left:288"><nobr><span class="ft5">If a connection can’t be made to a particular server, in the<br><b>Servers </b>list, a red cross displays next to the server. The Test Log<br>output shows the reason why the test failed in red text. For help<br>on how to resolve the connection problem, click <b>Help</b>.</span></nobr></DIV>
