<DIV style="position:absolute;top:709;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft4"><b>page 164</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:709;left:337"><nobr><span class="ft3">.)</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:742;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft17"><b>To add multiple servers by editing odbc.ini</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:775;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">In the section for the remote System DSN, specify the primary OOB<br>server and each fallback OOB server with the</span></nobr></DIV>
