<DIV style="position:absolute;top:395;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft6">Note that the bitmask values are given either in decimal or in<br>hexadecimal and the access control lists are separated simply by<br>spaces.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:476;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">Set</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:478;left:292"><nobr><span class="ft18">Flags</span></nobr></DIV>
