<DIV style="position:absolute;top:209;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">The Web Administrator facility lets you browse data sources for lists<br>of tables, table composition and rows of data in the tables.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:266;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft6">In order to browse system data sources on the machine where the<br>OOB Server is running you must enable the</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:292;left:614"><nobr><span class="ft18">AllowDBBrowse</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:314;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">configurable parameter on the Web Administrator <b>Configuration</b><br>screen.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:371;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft3">This converts the list of data source names on the</span></nobr></DIV>
