<DIV style="position:absolute;top:157;left:90"><nobr><span class="ft1"><b>APPENDIX A TECHNICAL REFERENCE</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:257;left:90"><nobr><span class="ft16">Additional information for the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:308;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft6">This section contains extra information relating to the deployment of<br>the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge (OOB).</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:365;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft5">It documents where the Easysoft ODBC-ODBC Bridge API differs<br>from other ODBC APIs, diagnostic functionality and tracing issues.</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:442;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft17"><b>Appendix Guide</b></span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:481;left:261"><nobr><span class="ft17"><b>•</b></span></nobr></DIV>
